cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.DL 

The paper describes the integration of automated reasoning and artificial intelligence tools with Mizar, a formal language for mathematics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of ATP systems, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the presentation of Mizar problems, which could be categorized under cs.SE (Software Engineering) or cs.PL (Programming Languages). Finally, the paper mentions the translation of Mizar to first-order ATP systems, which could be categorized under cs.DL (Digital Libraries).
